cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing tasks such as speech recognition and machine translation. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper specifically focuses on speech recognition. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper discusses the use of pre-trained language models to improve the performance of Seq2Seq models. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a broad category that could also apply as the paper deals with machine learning techniques applied to natural language processing tasks. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but could potentially apply as the paper discusses the use of language models to improve the performance of a system (i.e. the Seq2Seq model).
